  {
    question: 'Who should choose each?',
    answer: 'Klaviyo: Klaviyo is the heavyweight when a Shopify store has enough order volume to justify profile-based pricing and wants every… Shopify Email: Shopify Email works for basic newsletters and sale announcements. Stores focused on lifecycle revenue typically graduate…',
